    Merge "Adding support for Coraid AoE SANs Appliances."

commit a1deb1cdb0bc5e0af800f2e30be57e13d80d4b0e
Merge: 90971cd d17cc23
Author: Jenkins <jenkins@review.openstack.org>
Date:   Fri Feb 15 21:38:33 2013 +0000

