commit 56405da849bc76dc97e3e1bcbfda00d3b73a57cd
Author: Dan Prince <dprince@redhat.com>
Date:   Mon Sep 3 22:02:22 2012 -0400

    Remove Cheetah from pip-requires.
    
    We don't use Cheetah so no need to install it w/ pip.
    
