Date:   Tue Jul 17 04:28:02 2012 +0100

    Remove unused synchronization decorator
    
    This is only used on the compute and network side in Nova.
    
    Change-Id: I6211c32f585b1b5ff66d1a7a5f65dd25857d76f0
